  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nThe doc of the `IERC777.send` and `IERC777.burn` functions are inconsistent with the code. The doc references the parameter name `operatorData`, which is not in the code's parameters list. \r\n\r\nCould you please check it?\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/848fef5b6c39333a2f9f1fb352cca7c188c3754b/contracts/token/ERC777/IERC777.sol#L74-L75\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/848fef5b6c39333a2f9f1fb352cca7c188c3754b/contracts/token/ERC777/IERC777.sol#L96-L97\r\n\r\nThanks. ",
